            <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-[#FF5E15]" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M5 12h14M12 5l7 7-7 7"/></svg>
            {card.cta}
          </button>
        </div>
      ))}
    </div>
    <div class="text-center mt-10">
      <button type="button" class="popup-trigger inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-12 md:px-[100px] py-5 w-full md:w-auto bg-transparent text-white font-body text-[1.2rem] font-medium border-2 border-[#FF5E15] rounded-full hover:bg-[#FF5E15] transition-all duration-300 reveal-child">
        <svg class="w-4 h-4" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M5 12h14M12 5l7 7-7 7"/></svg>
        Get Started
      </button>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- ===================== SECTION 5: WHY CHOOSE DDAN ===================== -->
<section class="bg-black py-10 md:py-16 lg:py-20 px-5 reveal">
  <div class="max-w-[1280px] mx-auto grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center">
    <div>
      <h2 class="font-heading text-[#FF5E15] text-xl md:text-[3rem] font-semibold leading-[1.2] mb-3 text-center md:text-left reveal-child">Why Choose DDAN Hood Cleaning and Repair?</h2>
      <h3 class="font-heading text-white text-xl md:text-2xl font-semibold leading-snug mb-4 reveal-child">We do more than just clean; we fix, install, and protect your commercial kitchen's most vital system.</h3>
      <p class="text-[#DDDDDD] font-body text-base leading-relaxed mb-6 reveal-child">Unlike many "hood cleaners" who only provide surface-level work, DDAN offers end-to-end commercial kitchen exhaust system care. We meticulously clean every component to bare metal, expertly repair exhaust fan failures, professionally install new restaurant hood systems, and proactively solve ventilation problems before they can shut you down. Our work consistently meets and exceeds all health, fire, and safety standards, and every service is thoroughly documented with detailed reports for your records.</p>
      <a href="/contact/" class="inline-flex items-center flex-row-reverse gap-2.5 px-7 py-3 bg-[#032C5B] text-white font-body text-base font-medium rounded hover:bg-[#FF5E15] transition-all duration-300 reveal-child">
        Get Service Today
        <svg class="w-4 h-4" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M5 12h14M12 5l7 7-7 7"/></svg>
      </a>
    </div>
    <div class="reveal-child">
      <img src={`${HP}/restaurant-hood-cleaning-nashville-tn-DDAN-Hood-Cleaning-and-Repair-615-881-6968.jpg`} alt="restaurant hood cleaning nashville tn" width="720" height="960" class="w-full max-h-[560px] object-cover rounded-xl" loading="lazy" />
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

